既聲會變左Steinway &amp; Sons<br />\n偏偏音響界D人就會咁覺得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最搞笑係當你反對d人追求音響，就會有班人話你木耳，話你耳仔廢<br />\n都幾肯定唔少係賣耳筒耳音響既打手係度不斷洗人腦<br />\n就好似一條金屬線賣五位數然後話升級左之後聽完首歌變神仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你地覺得一條用得係音響既金屬線，「特別」得去邊呢？暴利成咁，係我都洗你地腦啦<br />\nd線仲貴過金呀痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大把賣耳筒線既講到d金屬好特別，又用哂d專業名詞咁，其實可能只係普通到不得了既一條普通金屬線，發發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇高性價比喇叭介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇其他人有"},{"pid":"61cbf6984dfcc78267f016c11c5bb0babad5a9f8","tid":2443921,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc3ce6c1aa21728e1d39341409798c761e45b79c","tid":2443921,"uid":2404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"音響係玩失真<br />\n<br />\n樓主大前提已經錯晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條曲線平咪「保真」"},{"pid":"6f3091bb4268dbb6aba739cdfa1b7c883140f7b7","tid":2443921,"uid":154152,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee9b10e18eaaecf6b50927a1dc4d7c31325013a5","tid":2443921,"uid":30067,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T22:49:09.000Z","msg":"Sony Music 旗下既ACG歌手都用垃圾錄音!?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"正正係sony旗下嗰D垃圾比例特別高<br />\n所以聽佢D人通常用翻sony機<br />\n<br />\n用其他player會清到聽出問題"},{"pid":"37b1984370e95c9a226763db6969b31145e2cc65","tid":2443921,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的確大部分都係垃圾錄音<br />\